    "description": "<p>\r\n\tServoConnect Systems is a pioneer in providing comprehensive solution on the range of Automation Products. By working with reputable brands, we distribute a wide range of industrial automation products representing Asia Pacific region.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tServoConnect Systems is One Stop Solution base System Integrator Division who provide professional services and optimal solutions for our valued customers. We help our customers from initial consultation, products specifications, system configuration, Design & product recommendation. We also extend our service to undertake turnkey project in Automation, Manufacturing, Marine Industries, Building Automation and Oil & Gas Segment.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tWe are a one stop Automation & Engineering Solution Provider !</p>\r\n",
